Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.52,0:00:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,A Sand...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.23,0:00:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What does this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.81,0:00:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know either...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.44,0:00:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But... he went missing right around the time Gaara was taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.86,0:00:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be that...\Nhe was a spy for the Akatsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.03,0:00:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.58,0:00:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He served on the council for four years...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.29,0:00:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Was he disguised with\Nthe Transformation Technique?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.34,0:00:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.42,0:00:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a technique of\Na much greater level...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.10,0:00:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The Fireball Technique was created\Nby the Uchiha Clan
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.39,0:00:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and they use it a lot by preference...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.39,0:00:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Katon: Goukakyuu no Jutsu!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.19,0:00:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And that technique was the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.04,0:01:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like you're done as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.96,0:01:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... I'm out of Chakra...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.59,0:01:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the Chakra we sacrificed was only about thirty percent...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.80,0:01:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Although it's a technique handy for creating exact duplicates of us,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.43,0:01:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,the quantity of Chakra\Nwe gave them wasn't that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.60,0:01:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And the techniques they can use are proportionate to that quantity.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.07,0:01:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was more than enough to buy us time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.81,0:02:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The technique wore off, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.19,0:02:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}However, we were able to buy quite a bit of time...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.11,0:02:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This should be enough...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.65,0:02:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well done, Itachi, Kisame.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.49,0:02:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's easy to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.31,0:02:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The two who became sacrifices and gave up their bodies for your technique were both my subordinates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.04,0:02:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You should be the one thanking me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.92,0:02:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With my Impersonation Technique,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.34,0:02:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}they were both able to become members of Akatsuki, although only for a short time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.35,0:02:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's almost time...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.66,0:04:29.62,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fscx95\fs36\bord4\blur4\fax0.18\fad(648,596)\pos(671,545)}The Secret of Jinchuuriki
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.70,0:04:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.12,0:04:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This means the real one is in the hideout, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.87,0:04:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we can say his goal was to stall us and to gather information.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.54,0:04:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that we know that,\Nthere's no point in hanging around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.21,0:04:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Let's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.26,0:04:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.26,0:04:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.02,0:04:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,They were clearly stalling for time...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.94,0:04:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,They've sure got a good technique...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.07,0:05:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I never realized... you were... fighting against people like this, Naruto.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.08,0:05:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Using a technique like this to stall us means...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.37,0:05:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,...they're undoubtedly already\Nextracting the Tailed Beast!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.17,0:05:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have time.\NWe must save Gaara right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.19,0:05:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,E-Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.83,0:05:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.01,0:05:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean... extract the Tailed Beast?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.93,0:05:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's likely that they're intention is to create a new Jinchuuriki using the One-Tail, Shukaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.98,0:05:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Jinchuuriki?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.57,0:05:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I explained before how the Tailed Beasts possess a power beyond human comprehension, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.91,0:05:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And how each land attempted to use them as military weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.25,0:06:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The Jinchuuriki... is what you might call... the one who controls that power.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.80,0:06:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But earlier you said...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.76,0:06:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Tailed Beasts have immense Chakra,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.76,0:06:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and during the era of Great War were used for military purposes by Hidden Villages around the world.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.72,0:06:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They competed to get their hands on them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.73,0:06:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But none was able to control that power which had surpassed human intelligence.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.57,0:06:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.37,0:06:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But in the past, there were those who attempted to control that power.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.33,0:06:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They attempted to control the Tailed Beast by sealing it inside people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.79,0:06:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,By doing so, they tried to suppress the extreme power of the Tailed Beast
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.76,0:06:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and then control that power.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.81,0:07:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And the ones with the\NTailed Beast sealed within them,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.17,0:07:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,in other words, people like Gaara\Nwere called the Jinchuuriki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.65,0:07:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The striking feature of the Jinchuuriki is how it utilizes unbelievable power by resonating with the Tailed Beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.66,0:07:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Including Gaara, there have been three Jinchuuriki in the history of the Sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.22,0:07:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.32,0:07:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So wars were fought often using the Jinchuuriki?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.32,0:07:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.82,0:07:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, the people who've\Nbeen turned into a Jinchuuriki...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.00,0:08:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,How can the Tailed Beast be extracted?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.80,0:08:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What's required is a Sealing Technique
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.84,0:08:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,with the ability to instantaneously balance the power of the Tailed Beast, in addition to plenty of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.48,0:08:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But if that's done, the Jinchuuriki...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.07,0:08:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.57,0:08:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.86,0:08:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The Jinchuuriki that has his Tailed Beast extracted...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.74,0:08:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,...dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.97,0:08:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The two people I mentioned earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.24,0:08:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sand Jinchuuriki other than Gaara
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.47,0:09:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,both had the Shukaku within them extracted and died as a result.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.40,0:09:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You're sentimental as always, huh? Sakura...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.12,0:09:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.58,0:09:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be saving Gaara!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.54,0:09:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I was concerned... about your...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.23,0:09:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.35,0:09:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naruto...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.24,0:10:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's from Big Sister, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.92,0:10:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't be moving yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.83,0:10:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not good for you in your condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.01,0:10:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm okay. I can at least walk...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.39,0:10:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, it seems we've been contacted by Granny Chiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.14,0:10:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't just lie around!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.85,0:10:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... So you've heard, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.15,0:10:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,As it happens, we've learned something terrible from her message.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.78,0:10:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yura was a spy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.16,0:10:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.86,0:10:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,A man who served on the council\Nfor four years wouldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.29,0:10:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But... now it makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.29,0:10:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,How the enemy broke through the village defenses that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.38,0:11:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm sure nobody imagined a man in charge of security would be an enemy spy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.22,0:11:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I thought we had thoroughly checked everyone out when Gaara became the Kazekage!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.73,0:11:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The person in question might've just been controlled by some kind of technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.57,0:11:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, it doesn't say anything about the most crucial thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.95,0:11:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,When's Gaara coming back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.24,0:11:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Having the Kazekage of one of the Five Great Nations no less
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.04,0:11:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,kidnapped by some bandits sets a bad example for the other lands!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.46,0:11:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And it seems one of them\Nis Sasori of the Red Sand!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.76,0:11:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be a tremendous disgrace if this gets out to the other lands!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.43,0:11:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If it becomes known that the Kazekage is missing,\Nwho knows when the neighboring lands will intervene.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.48,0:11:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Our most pressing need is to immediately elect a new Kazekage...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.65,0:11:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and make an effort to stabilize the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.98,0:12:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Gaara could still very well come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.90,0:12:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the fact is... it might just be better for the village if he doesn't come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.83,0:12:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you getting at?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.71,0:12:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Gaara is an unstable monster\Nwith the One-Tail inside him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.58,0:12:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We thought he would be easier to control if we made him the Kazekage...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.05,0:12:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But in the end, there's no telling when he might go out of control.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.05,0:12:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no mistaking he's trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.64,0:12:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Gaara originally resonated with\Nthe One-Tail, Shukaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.10,0:12:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But he's an unstable experiment we can hardly call complete...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.15,0:12:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's a failed creation who was even once ordered for assassination by his own father, the Fourth Kazekage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.90,0:12:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, some of the younger people just blindly admire him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.70,0:12:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But the fact is most of the people in this village are just scared of him and have no expectations of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.92,0:13:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Just try talking trash like that again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.13,0:13:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care if you {\i1}are{\i0} on the council.\NI won't allow it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.22,0:13:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, Kankuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.30,0:13:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're before the statues of the Kazekage!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.80,0:13:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a holy place!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.72,0:13:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Kankuro, your anger is understandable.\NBut there's an element of truth to what he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.23,0:13:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But the fact is... this isn't an issue of whether or not Gaara should be trusted.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.08,0:13:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Something like this happened\Nbefore a long time ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.12,0:13:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The Third Kazekage was kidnapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.87,0:13:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There were all kinds of conjecture in regards to the whereabouts of the Third Kazekage,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.80,0:13:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,war broke out and the lands were in chaos...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.59,0:13:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If only we paid our attention\Ntowards securing the village,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.30,0:13:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,rather than eagerly searching for the\NThird Kazekage, that wouldn't have happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.06,0:13:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why didn't you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.11,0:14:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The Third Kazekage was an exceptionally powerful Kazekage in our history.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.20,0:14:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And most importantly,\Na body was never found.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.04,0:14:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No one thought someone as powerful as he could have been killed that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.17,0:14:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Something like that must never happen again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.51,0:14:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why... we must consider the best interests of the village!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.43,0:14:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why the borders are being secured...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.14,0:14:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The village plunged into chaos when the enemy broke through our border by seizing the opportunity
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.45,0:14:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,while we were engaged in the search for the Third Kazekage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.13,0:14:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Our most pressing need is\Nto secure the borders.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.99,0:14:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But there was no reason to go out of your way to send Temari!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.70,0:14:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Kankuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.70,0:14:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.05,0:14:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Originally we were going to have {\i1}you{\i0} take on that mission as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.21,0:15:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But then you get yourself poisoned...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.79,0:15:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If we assign Gaara's siblings\Nto border patrol missions,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.17,0:15:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,the young people won't start talking about nonsense like rescuing Gaara.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.35,0:15:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Temari was dispatched to a place that's been infiltrated by the enemy many times in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.48,0:15:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We needed someone of Jonin\Nrank or higher to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.40,0:15:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.41,0:15:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But... But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.74,0:15:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Gaara's... Gaara's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.04,0:15:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,...my little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.40,0:16:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Zetsu, dispose of the two we used for Impersonation Technique.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.57,0:16:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Understood.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.28,0:16:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Itachi, tell me about the enemy's number and their features.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.29,0:16:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're a four-man squad with Kakashi Hatake, Sakura Haruno,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.92,0:16:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and the Nine-Tails Jinchuuriki Naruto Uzumaki from the Leaf,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.55,0:16:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and Chiyo, the Sand's advisor.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.47,0:16:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he say Granny Chiyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.65,0:16:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It seems he's still not quite accustomed to using the Giant Rasengan...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.88,0:17:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It looks like opening the Gate of Joy has left him quite exhausted...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.51,0:17:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Gai-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.59,0:17:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.93,0:17:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm always full of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.15,0:17:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Gai-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.44,0:17:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not okay at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.74,0:17:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.24,0:17:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He just used the Morning Peacock.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.74,0:17:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We should rest somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.63,0:17:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the place!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.39,0:18:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there really a point to us guarding this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.39,0:18:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Orders are orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.93,0:18:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll guard in 24-hour shifts as of now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.52,0:18:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.44,0:18:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.78,0:18:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Kakashi-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.49,0:18:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to take a short break here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.20,0:18:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a wise decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.16,0:18:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?! You're the one who\Nsaid we don't have time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.62,0:18:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If we waste time taking\Na break here, Gaara will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.58,0:18:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Compared to right before we encountered the fake Itachi, our pace has clearly slowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.47,0:18:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He's absolutely right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.47,0:18:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If we rest up here, ultimately we'll reach our destination faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.64,0:18:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And tomorrow, we might end up fighting the guys who took Gaara.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.15,0:18:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's best if we're at full strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.86,0:19:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.16,0:19:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is Kisame's, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.49,0:19:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He looks to be worth disposing of...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.25,0:19:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's get to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.54,0:19:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
